  30:Drivers/lvgl/src/draw/lv_draw_buf.h **** /**
  31:Drivers/lvgl/src/draw/lv_draw_buf.h ****  * Stride alignment for draw buffers.
  32:Drivers/lvgl/src/draw/lv_draw_buf.h ****  * It may vary between different color formats and hardware.
